<para style="q1">

<verse number="47" style="v" />Save us, Yahweh, our God.</para>

<para style="q1">Gather us from among the nations</para>

<para style="q1">so that we may give thanks to your holy name</para>

<para style="q1">and glory in your praises.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="48" style="v" />May Yahweh, the God of Israel, be praised</para>

<para style="q1">from everlasting to everlasting.</para>

<para style="q1">All the people said, "Amen."</para>

<para style="q1">Praise Yahweh.</para>

<para style="ms">Book Five</para>
